	<description>
	  <p>Current time in the world's largest financial centers</p>
	  <p>multiClock allows you to track the current time in major financial centers around the world</p>
	  <p>Features:</p>
	  <ul>
	    <li>It takes into account the transition to summer / winter time in selected cities.</li>
      <li>Indispensable for Forex traders away from the trading monitor.
        It helps to navigate the start and end time of trading sessions on local financial exchanges.</li>
      <li>It has a simple and clear interface.</li>
      <li>A customizable list of financial centers for display.</li>
      <li>A customizable online multilingual translation of the application interface.</li>
	  </ul>
	</description>

